thread.title_full: Easy Signs reviewed by Kerry - Upper Yarra TOWN Club

author: Kerry - Upper Yarra TOWN Club
title: Kerry - Upper Yarra TOWN Club
text: I was very nervous about receiving the banner as I was spending our clubs funds and really wanted it to be perfect. Well I can advise that I was very impressed with the quality and the overall appearance of our banner. When I showed it to our members, they were very impressed and said it was well worth the money. The staff were very patient as I kept making alterations until it was exactly what I wanted. Thanks Easy Signs!
